sources.title: Robot Pilot (1941) ACTION-THRILLER
sources.description:
Stars: Forrest Tucker, Carol Hughes, Evelyn Brent 
 Director: William Beaudine

 A test pilot and his weather observer develop a "robot" control so airplanes can be flown without pilots, but enemy agents get wind of it and try to steal it or destroy it. (a.k.a. Emergency Landing)
